search_results.title: Gunnar Dybwad
search_results.snippet: Gunnar Dybwad (1909–2001) was an American professor and advocate for the rights of people with disabilities, particularly developmental disabilities.

search_results.title: Gunnar Heinsohn
search_results.snippet: Gunnar Heinsohn (21 November 1943 – 16 February 2023) was a German author, sociologist and economist and professor emeritus at the University of Bremen

search_results.title: Professor Gunnar Broberg (1942-2022)
search_results.snippet: Professor Gunnar Broberg, a masterly scholar of Carl Linnaeus, passed away on Saturday 30 April at the age of 79.
